type: Tutorial Step - Let's Run the Command!

definition.text: Let's get on with the task at hand! Copy the command below, paste it on the search/command box, and hit Enter!

paragraphs.text: A GitHub sing in dialog should pop-up offering you to authenticate with your token or password. Just follow the process with either!
The latest version of Git is required for this to work! If you have issues authenticating with the latest version, restarting the PC may help.
